::Koj::

Koj goes to down the lower levels of the CF where he created his lair. He 
stops out side his chamber and gets on the ships intercom "Make me aware of 
any battles Koj out." As he enters the chamber he climbs into a his private 
Cr pool and starts to heal.

::Inu-Yasha::

Inu is still kinda shocked Koj is a Dragon Master. Opens the bay doors in 
the lair and goes out to his perch letting his breath Weapons recharge. "I 
guess I could start Koj's trainning but a Dragon master that is rude cocky a 
smartass Feh!" Inu-Yasha Laughing as a bird lands on his shoulder "He maybe 
the greastest one yet because he breaks the norm and does thing his way 
not." Inu-Yasha sits on the perch watching the afternoon sun. As he waits 
removes a Diamond form his collar and eats it.
